servers/ — ARD Treasure Hunt MCP servers (© Andreas Adner)
----------------------------------------------------------
The four services under `servers/` — `challenge1-mcp`, `challenge2-mcp`,
`challenge3-mcp`, and `challenge3-search` — are the work of **Andreas Adner**
(https://nullpointer.se/), vendored from his public Agentic Resource Discovery
treasure-hunt repository so this .NET toolkit can stand up a *self-hosted* hunt
(locally via .NET Aspire, and on Azure via IaC).

They remain Andreas's work and are included here with attribution. The only change
from the originals is a single, clearly-commented env-overridable constant in
`servers/challenge3-search/src/index.ts` (`CARD3_URL`), so the search service can
point at your own infrastructure instead of the original Azure host. Everything else
is byte-for-byte as published.

Andreas's repository did not carry an explicit license at the time of vendoring. This
copy exists to power the self-hosting feature with full credit to the author. If you
fork or redistribute these servers, please keep this attribution and check reuse terms
